title: Crossing Trump: 2 S.C. Republicans take different approaches - The Associated Press - en Español
content: Crossing Trump: 2 S.C. Republicans take different approaches  The Associated Press - en EspañolView Full Coverage on Google News
description: FLORENCE, S.C. (AP) — Under pressure recently to prove her loyalty to Donald Trump, Rep. Nancy Mace traveled to New York to film a social media video outside Trump Tower reminding her South Carolina constituents that she was one of the former president's “earliest supporters."
